\v 3 Ngakho, kwathi sebephelekezelwe libandla\x + 20.38. 21.5. Roma 15.24. 1 Kor. 16.6,11. 2 Kor. 1.16. Tit. 3.13. 3 Joha. 6. Seb. 17.15.\x*, badabula iFenekiya\x + 11.19.\x* leSamariya\x + 1.8.\x*, balandisa \add ngo\add*kuphenduka kwabezizwe\x + 14.27. 15.12.\x*; benzela bonke abazalwane intokozo enkulu\x + 15.3,22,23. Joha. 21.23.\x*.
\v 4 Kwathi sebefikile eJerusalema, bemukelwa libandla labaphostoli\x + 21.17. Luka 8.40.\x* labadala\x + 15.4,6,22,23. 11.30.\x*, njalo balandisa ukuthi zingakanani izinto uNkulunkulu ayezenze labo\x + 14.27. 15.3,12. 21.19.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa kwasukuma abanye abakholwayo abangabehlelo labaFarisi, besithi: Kufanele uku\add ba\add*soka, lokubalaya bagcine umlayo kaMozisi\x + 15.5. Gal. 5.1,2. Fil. 3.2. Kol. 2.11.\x*.
