\v 8 Njalo uNkulunkulu umazi wenhliziyo\x + 1.24. 1 Sam. 16.7.\x* wabafakazela\x + 14.3.\x*, ebanika uMoya oyiNgcwele\x + 10.44.\x*, lanjengathi\x + 10.47.\x*;
\v 9 futhi kehlukanisanga phakathi kwethu labo\x + 10.35.\x*, ehlambulula inhliziyo zabo\x + Hlab. 51.10. Seb. 10.15. 11.9. 2 Kor. 7.1. 1 Kor. 1.2. 1 Pet. 1.22. Joha. 13.10. Jak. 1.21.\x* ngokholo\x + 10.43.\x*.
\v 10 Pho-ke limlingelani uNkulunkulu\x + 5.9.\x*, ngokubeka ijogwe entanyeni yabafundi, obaba bethu kanye lathi esingabanga lamandla okulithwala\x + Gal. 5.1. Mat. 23.4.\x*?
