\v 20 kodwa sibabhalele ukuthi bazile amanyala ezithombe\x + Dan. 1.8. Mal. 1.7,12. Seb. 15.29. Hlab. 106.28. Hez. 4.13,14.\x*, lokufeba\x + 1 Kor. 10.7,8. 1 Pet. 4.3,4. Isam. 2.14,20. 1 Kor. 6.18.\x*, lokukhanyiweyo\x + Levi 3.17.\x*, legazi\x + Levi 3.17.\x*.
