\v 22 Kwasekubonakala kukuhle kubaphostoli lakubadala\x + 15.2.\x* kanye lebandla lonke, ukuthuma amadoda akhethiweyo phakathi kwabo eAntiyoki loPawuli loBarnabasi\x + 15.23,30,35. 11.26.\x*; \add babe\add* ngoJudasi othiwa futhi nguBarsaba\x + 1.23.\x*, loSilasi\x + 15.34.\x*, amadoda angabakhokheli\x + Luka 22.26.\x* phakathi kwabazalwane\x + 15.1.\x*,
