\v 27 Ngakho sithumile uJudasi loSilasi\x + 15.22,32.\x*, abazakuthi labo ngelizwi \add lomlomo\f + \fk ngomlomo: \fl Gr. \fq ngelizwi.\f*\add* balitshele izinto ezifananayo.
\v 28 Ngoba kwabonakala kukuhle kuMoya oNgcwele, lakithi, ukuthi singalethesi umthwalo omkhulu, ngaphandle kwalezizinto ezifunekayo\x + 15.19. 15.28. Luka 1.3.\x*:
\v 29 Ukuthi lizile okuhlatshelwe izithombe\x + 15.20. 21.25. 1 Kor. 8.1,4,7,10.10.19,28. Isam. 2.14,20. Seb. 15.20.\x*, legazi\x + 15.20. 21.25.\x*, lokukhanyiweyo, lokufeba; lezizinto nxa lizazizila, lizabe lenze kuhle. Salani kuhle\x + 23.30.\x*.
