\s Ukwehlukana kukaPawuli loBarnabasi
\p
\v 36 Emva kwensuku ezithile uPawuli wasesithi kuBarnabasi: Ake sibuye sihambele abazalwane bethu emizini yonke, lapho esatshumayela khona ilizwi leNkosi, \add sibone\add* ukuthi bahlezi njani\x + 13.4,13,14,51. 14.1,6,24,25.\x*.
\v 37 UBarnabasi wasehlosa ukuthatha uJohane, othiwa nguMarko, ahambe labo\x + 15.39. 12.12.\x*.
\v 38 Kodwa uPawuli wacabanga ukuthi kufanele ukuthi bangamthathi ahambe labo lowo owabatshiya\x + 13.13.\x* ePamfiliya, kaze aya labo emsebenzini.
\v 39 Kwasekuvela ukuphikisana okukhulu, baze behlukana phakathi; uBarnabasi\x + Kol. 4.10.\x* wasethatha uMarko\x + 15.39. 12.12.\x* wahamba laye ngomkhumbi, baya eKuprosi\x + 4.36.\x*.
